{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModelProtocol"]]},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"itemsChanged","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"position"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"removed","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"added"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO17MenuModelProtocolPAAE12itemsChanged8position7removed5addedySi_S2itF","extendedModule":"GIO","title":"itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/menumodelprotocol\/itemschanged(position:removed:added:)"]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModelProtocol\/itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"text":"Requests emission of the [MenuModel](\/\/documentation\/gio\/menumodel\/onitemschanged(flags:handler:) signal on ","type":"text"},{"code":"model","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"itemsChanged","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"position"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"removed"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"added","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This function should never be called except by "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModel","isActive":true},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"subclasses.  Any other calls to this function will very likely lead","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a violation of the interface of the model."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The implementation should update its internal representation of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"menu before emitting the signal.  The implementation should further"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"expect to receive queries about the new state of the menu (and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"particularly added menu items) while signal handlers are running."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The implementation must dispatch this call directly from a mainloop","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"entry and not in response to calls – particularly those from the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModel"},{"type":"text","text":" API.  Said another way: the menu must not change while"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"user code is running without returning to the mainloop."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/MenuModelProtocol/itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)":{"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/menumodelprotocol\/itemschanged(position:removed:added:)","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Requests emission of the [MenuModel](\/\/documentation\/gio\/menumodel\/onitemschanged(flags:handler:) signal on "},{"code":"model","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"itemsChanged","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"position","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removed","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"added","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModelProtocol\/itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)","title":"itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/MenuModelProtocol":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/menumodelprotocol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MenuModelProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"code":"GMenuModel","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" represents the contents of a menu — an ordered list of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"menu items. The items are associated with actions, which can be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"activated through them. Items can be grouped in sections, and may","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"have submenus associated with them. Both items and sections usually","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"have some representation data, such as labels or icons. The type of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the associated action (ie whether it is stateful, and what kind of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"state it has) can influence the representation of the item."}],"title":"MenuModelProtocol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModelProtocol","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"MenuModelProtocol"}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/MenuModel":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MenuModel"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModel","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/menumodel","title":"MenuModel","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"MenuModel","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GMenuModel"},{"type":"text","text":" represents the contents of a menu — an ordered list of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"menu items. The items are associated with actions, which can be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"activated through them. Items can be grouped in sections, and may","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"have submenus associated with them. Both items and sections usually","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"have some representation data, such as labels or icons. The type of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the associated action (ie whether it is stateful, and what kind of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"state it has) can influence the representation of the item."}]}}}